title: Re roll
body: So i re rolled 3 chapms and got naut and when i go to champs its says i dont own him whats going on?

replies.body: Looking into his for you, I don't see any hextech rerolls.  The last action was back on the 9th when you unlocked 2 championship rolls.  What materials were you rerolling for the unlock?  Is it still in your inventory?  Let me know.
Sorry to bother you I just found out it was a different account.
